OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772917925
OL,3,CBonfire building material appears on
OL,4,Csite amid warnings of asbestos
OL,6,FA controversial bonfire site in South
OL,7,FBelfast is under the spotlight again
OL,8,Fafter it was revealed that pallets are
OL,9,Fbeing stockpiled on the ring-fenced
OL,10,Fand privately-owned land.
OL,12,FThe Environment Minister yesterday
OL,13,Fwarned the public not to step onto the
OL,14,Flocked site amid concerns that
OL,15,Fasbestos fragments remain despite
OL,16,Fremedial work being carried out to
OL,17,Fremove the hazardous material.
OL,19,FLast summer there were pleas not to
OL,20,Flight the bonfire due to the health
OL,21,Fwarnings about asbestos.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772917925
OL,3,CBonfire building material appears on
OL,4,Csite amid warnings of asbestos
OL,6,FIt went up in flames anyway.
OL,8,FNo amount of public warnings, legal
OL,9,Fchallenges, or the proximity to an
OL,10,Felectricity substation that powers
OL,11,Fboth the Royal and City hospitals
OL,12,Fcould change their minds.
OL,14,FThe controversy looks set to be re-
OL,15,Fignited with the reappearance of
OL,16,Fbonfire-building materials amid a
OL,17,Fwarning from the Environment Minister
OL,18,Fthat fragments of asbestos remain on
OL,19,Fsite despite remedial work by the
OL,20,Flandowner.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
