CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772917925
OL,3,CBonfire building material appears on
OL,4,Csite amid warnings of asbestos
OL,6,FAndrew Muir MLA, Environment Minister
OL,7,Fsaid: "It appears that people have
OL,8,Fentered the site.
OL,10,F"The pallets have been deposited
OL,11,Fthere. Unauthorized access to the site
OL,12,Fcould amount to a criminal offense.
OL,14,F"Given the ongoing risk to the safety
OL,15,Fof people accessing the site, the
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland Environment Agency
OL,17,Fwould again urge members of the public
OL,18,Fnot to access it under any
OL,19,Fcircumstances.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772917925
OL,3,CBonfire building material appears on
OL,4,Csite amid warnings of asbestos
OL,6,F"I, as Minister today, would urge
OL,7,Flocal elected representatives to
OL,8,Fprovide the leadership needed to
OL,9,Fensure that people obey the law and
OL,10,Fheed the warnings issued to keep
OL,11,Fpeople off the site."
OL,13,FCllr Tracy Kelly is the DUP councillor
OL,14,Ffor the area, she said: "Well, I'd
OL,15,Flike to know why we're a year later
OL,16,Fand they haven't been cleared? Yeah, I
OL,17,Fwould like to know that."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
