PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772917925
OL,3,CBonfire building material appears on
OL,4,Csite amid warnings of asbestos
OL,6,FShe continued: "Any child or any
OL,7,Fperson to be on a site that's
OL,8,Fdangerous, and this is why myself and
OL,9,Fothers have called for it to be
OL,10,Fcleared and to be made safe.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
