FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772917925
OL,3,CBonfire building material appears on
OL,4,Csite amid warnings of asbestos
OL,6,F"And no child should be anywhere near
OL,7,Fanything dangerous. But when you're
OL,8,Ftelling a community in 2011 that this
OL,9,Fproperty has been taken away, the
OL,10,Fasbestos has been left as the lowest
OL,11,Fpoint and it's not dangerous`and now
OL,12,Fyou're telling them, "Oh, don't go
OL,13,Fanywhere near the site, there's
OL,14,Ffragments of asbestos on it." I would
OL,15,Fjust ask Minister Muir to clarify
OL,16,Fexactly what is on there and when it's
OL,17,Fgoing to be cleared."
OL,19,FA criminal investigation into the
OL,20,Fcontamination is still ongoing.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
